After 3 minutes add the ginger and garlic.

0:02:41.305,0:02:43.433
# 料头爆出香味之后开始调味
After the aroma comes out, start seasoning.

0:02:43.433,0:02:45.620
# 加入少许生抽酱油从锅边淋入
Add a bit light soy sauce from the side of the wok.

0:02:45.780,0:02:47.833
# 加入适量的蚝油调咸鲜味
Add some oyster sauce to adjust the taste.

0:02:48.436,0:02:50.265
# 加入少许的老抽调色
Add a touch of dark soy sauce for the color

0:02:51.488,0:02:54.448
# 小火翻炒均匀之后再加入切好的大红椒段
Stir-fry everything on low heat, then add the red pepper.

0:03:00.340,0:03:03.192
